snippet: Wilson Chandler scored 21 points, Ty Lawson had 20, and the Denver Nuggets snapped a six-game losing streak by beating the Dallas Mavericks 115-110 on Wednesday night....

headline.print_headline: Nuggets End Skid by Beating Mavericks 115-110
headline.main: Nuggets End Skid by Beating Mavericks 115-110

lead_paragraph: Wilson Chandler scored 21 points, Ty Lawson had 20, and the Denver Nuggets snapped a six-game losing streak by beating the Dallas Mavericks 115-110 on Wednesday night.
